<br>
This entire game is based on a mechanic where you get a message when you use a skill.  They are even going back and changing some spells that lack those messages (fear animal anyone?).  To have one skill that doesn't display a message because "it's a rogue thing" is both inconsistent, and pretty sad for us rogues.  I'd hate to think that our defining characteristic is that we get a message when using a skill and nobody else gets <i>our message</i>.<br>
<br>
